sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ManualEntryScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>StartWorkoutSession / EndWorkoutSession
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>WorkoutSession
  A->>B: enter type, duration, metrics - tap SAVE
  B->>C: startSession(type, connectedDeviceId = null)
  C->>E: endSession(sessionId, manual metrics)
  note right of E: null connectedDeviceId<br/>marks a manual entry
  E-->>C: saved session (xp_gained)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (done)
  B-->>A: session appears in History
  note over E: DESCOPED / removed from the FYP build (US13) — a free-text entry<br/>let users farm XP/level/streak with no sensor evidence (reconciliation §C8).<br/>Diagram retained for traceability — all progress now needs a captured session.
